===== Involved rules descriptions:

[iamf][Rule #10] id: assert-mix-presentation-obu
Section 3.7
Mix Presentation OBU checks:
- mix_presentation_id SHALL be unique within an IA Sequence.
- num_sub_mixes SHALL NOT be set to 0.
- num_audio_elements SHALL NOT be set to 0.
- There SHALL be no duplicate values of audio_element_id within one Mix Presentation.
- Each sub-mix SHALL include loudness for Stereo.

[iamf][Rule #11] id: assert-mix-presentation-loudness
Section 3.7.4
Loudness Info checks:
- There SHALL be no duplicate values of anchor_element within one LoudnessInfo.

[iamf][Rule #12] id: assert-mix-presentation-tags
Section 3.7.5
Mix Presentation Tags checks:
- There SHALL be at most one instance of content_language tag.
- content_language tag value SHALL conform to ISO-639-2-Codes (3-letter code).

